    <sys:String x:Key="LOCPlayState_SettingConfiguredInformationHotkeyLabel">Configured Information hotkey:</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOCPlayState_SettingConfiguredInformationHotkeyTooltip">Shows a notification that displays the current pause state and other information of the active game</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOCPlayState_SettingChangeHotkeyButtonLabel">更改热键</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOCPlayState_SettingPressHotkeyPromtButtonLabel">请按热键</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOCPlayState_SettingNotes" xml:space="preserve">Notes:

The configured hotkeys won't be able to be used in other applications.
Changing this setting requires restart.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOCPlayState_SettingsWinNotificationNote" xml:space="preserve">If you have Focus Assist enabled when playing a game and fullscreen mode, you have to add Playnite to priority list in order to receive Windows notifications and configure them to allow to display them.

This feature is only supported on Windows 10 and Windows 11</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOCPlayState_MessageWinStyleNotificationsFirstSetup" xml:space="preserve">PlayState has added support to display notifications as native windows notifications. This is enabled by default and can be changed from the extension settings.

For better compatibility with games, some adjustments to your Windows configuration is required. A link that contains the the instructions for this will be opened after closing this dialog.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOCPlayState_SettingHelpLabel">Help</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOCPlayState_SettingSubstractSuspendedPlaytimeOnStoppedLabel">当游戏停止时从游玩时间中扣除其挂起的时间。</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOCPlayState_SettingSubstractSuspendedPlaytimeOnStoppedTooltip">通过仅保留游戏未挂起时的时间并计入游戏的游玩时间，来帮助得到更精确的游玩时间值。</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOCPlayState_SettingSubstractOnlyNonLibraryGamesLabel">仅对不被库插件管理的游戏执行</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOCPlayState_SettingGlobalOnlySuspendPlaytimeLabel">仅挂起全局（而非游戏进程）的游玩时间记录</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOCPlayState_SettingGlobalOnlySuspendPlaytimeTooltip" xml:space="preserve">通过启用此选项，在使用已配置的热键时，所有游戏都不会被挂起，但时间被记录（并在游戏停止时从游玩时间扣除）。
    
也可以单独应用于某一个游戏，方法是为其添加一个“[PlayState] Suspend playtime only”的功能特色。</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOCPlayState_SettingGlobalShowWindowsNotificationsStyleLabel">Show native Windows notifications instead of Playnite notification window</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOCPlayState_SettingGlobalShowWindowsNotificationsStyleTooltip">By enabling this option, games will show native Windows notifications instead of Playnite notification window.</sys:String>
